---
// Social Proof section - Research-backed stats with visual polish
---

<section class="social-proof section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="label label-coral">Why It Works</span>
      <h2>Accountability is the missing ingredient</h2>
      <p>The research behind why social commitment outperforms willpower alone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-grid reveal">
      <div class="stat-card stat-card-primary">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-number" data-count="65" data-suffix="%">65%</span>
        <span class="stat-label">more likely to reach your goal when you commit to a partner</span>
        <span class="stat-source">American Society of Training &amp; Development</span>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card stat-card-green">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-number" data-count="21">21</span>
        <span class="stat-label">days is the average time to form a new lasting habit</span>
        <span class="stat-source">Behavioral science research</span>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-card stat-card-purple">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="stat-number" data-count="4" data-suffix="h">4h</span>
        <span class="stat-label">grace period so life doesn't ruin a streak you've earned</span>
        <span class="stat-source">Built into TinyAct</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="proof-callout reveal">
      <div class="proof-icon" aria-hidden="true">💡</div>
      <p>When your partner's streak <strong>depends on you showing up</strong>, motivation stops being optional.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .social-proof {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Stats Grid */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-900) 0%, var(--gray-800) 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    color: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
  }

  .stat-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
  }

  .stat-card-primary::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--coral), var(--coral-light)); }
  .stat-card-green::before   { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--green-dark), var(--green-light)); }
  .stat-card-purple::before  { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--purple), var(--purple-light)); }

  .stat-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .stat-card-primary .stat-icon {
    background: rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.15);
    color: var(--coral-light);
  }

  .stat-card-green .stat-icon {
    background: rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.15);
    color: var(--green-light);
  }

  .stat-card-purple .stat-icon {
    background: rgba(148, 102, 222, 0.15);
    color: var(--purple-light);
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .stat-card-primary .stat-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--coral), var(--coral-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .stat-card-green .stat-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .stat-card-purple .stat-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--purple-light));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .stat-source {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Proof callout */
  .proof-callout {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.06), rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.02));
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .proof-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .proof-callout p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .proof-callout strong {
    color: var(--coral);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .stats-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 440px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .proof-callout {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }

    .proof-callout p {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }
  }
</style>
